---
const painPoints = [
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-bear" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" /></svg>`,
    title: "You're Trading Alone",
    body: "No one to bounce ideas off. No one to gut-check your entries. You stare at charts solo, second-guess yourself, and close out positions you should've held.",
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-bear" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>`,
    title: "You're Missing Entries",
    body: "By the time you see the setup on TikTok, the move already happened. You chase. You enter late. The alert came and went, and you weren't in the room.",
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-bear" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>`,
    title: "You Have No One to Learn From",
    body: "YouTube videos and Reddit threads aren't mentorship. You're piecing together a strategy from ten different sources that contradict each other. No structure. No feedback.",
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-navy-950">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        You Already Know the Market Moves.
        <span class="text-bear"> You're Just Seeing Them Too Late.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      {painPoints.map((point) => (
        <div class="card-feature fade-in group">
          <div class="mb-4" set:html={point.icon} />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-3">{point.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">{point.body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
